{"tid":611220,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"染完髮又要日日gel頭應該點好？","createTime":"2018-03-30T18:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T22:49:00.000Z","uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8267d2764905d2b16e9f3aa6d213ed857263acda","tid":611220,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:02:36.000Z","msg":"前幾日染完灰色<br />\n淨係漂左一次啲色都上得幾好<br />\n但小弟係慣左日日gel頭出街嘅<br />\n之前未染髮嗰陣就每次gel前同訓前都會洗頭<br />\n但而家驚洗得多甩色臨訓前都冇洗頭<br />\nGel住咁訓<br />\n第二朝起身再洗頭同gel頭<br />\n但總係覺得咁樣keep住落去唔係辦法<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩方法可以冇咁快甩色之餘又可以唔洗gel住訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbab3010b026c22dc888e624a5c305a0b037dc1","tid":611220,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解會有負評嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361d7f1499e7a6d9789d275f514c7b03034a936e","tid":611220,"uid":25136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"有護色洗髮水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e016a3758a7ab85082e8075b5784b12135c1e012","tid":611220,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"361d7f1499e7a6d9789d275f514c7b03034a936e","tid":611220,"uid":25136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"有護色洗髮水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:24:02.000Z","msg":"有用到，但始終都係驚會甩得快"},{"pid":"8211dc37ef4edbd34c4f0043cb84a9a4df5ca23a","tid":611220,"uid":35667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:24:47.000Z","msg":"準備脫髮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0a9